---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<BaseLayout
  title="白泽明理，让每个组织都能明白 AI，用好 AI"
  description="设计型 AI 咨询：从接入、工程到交付，帮团队设计一条可验证、可复用的 AI 使用路径。只给方案、规范与蓝图，落地执行留给你的团队。"
  path="/"
>
  <div class="bz-hero-split">
    <div class="bz-hero-split__copy">
      <p class="bz-hero-split__eyebrow">Formal eXplainable AI</p>
      <h1 class="bz-hero-split__title bz-logotype">白泽明理</h1>
      <p class="bz-hero-split__sub">让复杂 AI 变得可解释、可验证、可落地。</p>
      <p class="bz-hero-split__body">不是把 AI 工具卖给团队，而是帮团队设计可控的使用路径。从稳定接入、工程化到端到端交付，把 AI 变成可验证、可复用的组织能力。</p>
      <div class="bz-hero-split__actions">
        <a class="bz-button bz-button--primary bz-button--lg" href={`${base}contact`}>预约 AI 落地诊断</a>
        <a class="bz-button bz-button--secondary bz-button--lg" href={`${base}services`}>查看服务路径</a>
      </div>
      <p class="bz-hero-split__meta">上海 / 远程，帮团队从尝鲜 AI 走向稳定使用 AI</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bz-hero-split__visual" aria-hidden="true">
      <img class="bz-hero-split__mark" src={`${base}baize-mark.png`} alt="" />
      <span class="bz-hero-split__doodle bz-hero-split__doodle--cloud">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 120 56" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 42c-6 0-8-9-1-12 1-9 14-11 19-4 3-10 20-9 22 1 5-6 17-4 16 5 9-1 13 8 5 11z" /></svg>
      </span>
      <span class="bz-hero-split__doodle bz-hero-split__doodle--seal">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="8" y="9" width="44" height="43" rx="3" /><path d="M22 22c7 9 7 15 16 18" opacity="0.85" /><circle cx="24" cy="40" r="1.8" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" /></svg>
      </span>
      <span class="bz-hero-split__doodle bz-hero-split__doodle--spark">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M30 5c2 18 7 23 25 25-18 2-23 7-25 25-2-18-7-23-25-25 18-2 23-7 25-25z" /></svg>
      </span>
      <span class="bz-hero-split__doodle bz-hero-split__doodle--wave">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 120 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M4 12q12-11 24 0t24 0 24 0 24 0" /><path d="M4 27q12-11 24 0t24 0 24 0 24 0" opacity="0.7" /></svg>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="bz-logowall" aria-label="团队常用的 AI 工具">
    <div class="bz-logowall__inner">
      <span class="bz-logowall__label">团队已在使用</span>
      <ul class="bz-logowall__list">
        <li>Codex</li><li>Claude Code</li><li>Cursor</li><li>GitHub Copilot</li><li>VS Code</li><li>Skills</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services" class="bz-rail-section">
    <div class="bz-rail-grid">
      <aside aria-label="Services section label">
        <div class="bz-rail-label">Services</div>
        <div class="bz-rail-bar"></div>
      </aside>
      <div class="bz-home-intro">
        <div>
          <h2 class="bz-home-heading">不是把 AI 工具卖给团队，而是帮团队设计可控的使用路径。</h2>
          <p class="bz-home-lead">五项服务串成一条阶梯：先接入，再工程化，最后设计出从想法到产品的交付路径。白泽只给方案、规范与蓝图，落地执行留给你的团队。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bz-tier">
          <div class="bz-tier__head">
            <span class="bz-tier__step">01 · 接入 Access</span>
            <h3 class="bz-tier__name">先把 AI 稳定、可控、可审计地接进来。</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bz-cell-grid bz-cell-grid--3" aria-label="接入层服务">
            <article class="bz-cell">
              <div class="bz-cell__n">01</div>
              <h3 class="bz-cell__t">Codex 中转站搭建</h3>
              <p class="bz-cell__b">给团队一个稳定、可控、可审计的 Codex 使用入口，不用各自找账号。</p>
              <div class="bz-cell__out">交付物 · 接入架构 + 权限规则 + 落地指导</div>
            </article>
            <article class="bz-cell">
              <div class="bz-cell__n">02</div>
              <h3 class="bz-cell__t">LLM API 网关设计</h3>
              <p class="bz-cell__b">团队所有 AI 调用的统一入口：鉴权、路由、限流、成本和审计一处管好。</p>
              <div class="bz-cell__out">交付物 · 网关蓝图 + 路由降级策略 + 审计设计</div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bz-tier">
          <div class="bz-tier__head">
            <span class="bz-tier__step">02 · 工程 Engineering</span>
            <h3 class="bz-tier__name">再把 AI 变成可迭代、可验证的工程能力。</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bz-cell-grid bz-cell-grid--3" aria-label="工程层服务">
            <article class="bz-cell">
              <div class="bz-cell__n">03</div>
              <h3 class="bz-cell__t">AI 研发流设计</h3>
              <p class="bz-cell__b">把 AI 编程纳入需求、实现、测试、评审、文档的真实流程，而不是个人自由发挥。</p>
              <div class="bz-cell__out">交付物 · 研发 SOP + 使用规范 + 验收标准</div>
            </article>
            <article class="bz-cell">
              <div class="bz-cell__n">04</div>
              <h3 class="bz-cell__t">Loop Engineering 设计</h3>
              <p class="bz-cell__b">让 AI 像有经验的工程师一样，先自查再交付，每一轮都比上一轮更准。</p>
              <div class="bz-cell__out">交付物 · 回路架构 + 评估体系 + 可复用模板</div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bz-tier bz-tier--end">
          <div class="bz-tier__head">
            <span class="bz-tier__step">03 · 交付 Delivery</span>
            <h3 class="bz-tier__name">最终把能力设计成真实产品与增长路径。</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bz-cell-grid" aria-label="交付层服务">
            <article class="bz-cell">
              <div class="bz-cell__n">05</div>
              <h3 class="bz-cell__t">想法到产品端到端交付设计</h3>
              <p class="bz-cell__b">一条从想法到可用产品、每一步都能验收的路线图；白泽只做设计，执行交给你的团队。</p>
              <div class="bz-cell__out">交付物 · 交付蓝图 + 里程碑 + 验收标准</div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="method" class="bz-rail-section bz-rail-section--alt">
    <div class="bz-rail-grid">
      <aside aria-label="Method section label">
        <div class="bz-rail-label">Method</div>
        <div class="bz-rail-bar"></div>
      </aside>
      <div class="bz-home-intro">
        <div>
          <h2 class="bz-home-heading">先明理，再落地。先边界，再自动化。</h2>
          <p class="bz-home-lead">白泽明理的交付逻辑不是堆模型和工具，而是把 AI 能做什么、不能做什么、谁来审查、如何复用讲清楚。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bz-flow" aria-label="白泽明理方法论流程">
          <div class="bz-flow__step">
            <span class="bz-flow__node">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7" />
                <path d="M16 16l6 6" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="bz-flow__stage">Diagnose</span>
            <h3 class="bz-flow__title">诊断团队当前 AI 使用状态</h3>
            <p class="bz-flow__desc">识别工具分散、流程断点、权限风险和知识不可复用的问题。</p>
            <span class="bz-flow__out">输出 · 落地优先级与风险边界</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bz-flow__step">
            <span class="bz-flow__node">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="3" width="8" height="8" />
                <rect x="15" y="3" width="8" height="8" />
                <rect x="3" y="15" width="8" height="8" />
                <rect x="15" y="15" width="8" height="8" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="bz-flow__stage">Build</span>
            <h3 class="bz-flow__title">搭建最小可用的组织级工作流</h3>
            <p class="bz-flow__desc">把 AI 接入真实研发、内容、运营或知识处理任务，而不是另起一套演示流程。</p>
            <span class="bz-flow__out">输出 · SOP、模板与验收标准</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bz-flow__step">
            <span class="bz-flow__node">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M13 3l10 5-10 5-10-5z" />
                <path d="M3 13l10 5 10-5" />
                <path d="M3 18l10 5 10-5" opacity="0.55" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="bz-flow__stage">Compound</span>
            <h3 class="bz-flow__title">把有效方法沉淀成可复用资产</h3>
            <p class="bz-flow__desc">将团队经验写成 Skills、工作流说明和项目上下文，让每次使用都能继承已有方法。</p>
            <span class="bz-flow__out">输出 · 团队知识资产</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="notes" class="bz-rail-section">
    <div class="bz-rail-grid">
      <aside aria-label="Proof section label">
        <div class="bz-rail-label">Proof</div>
        <div class="bz-rail-bar"></div>
      </aside>
      <div class="bz-home-intro">
        <h2 class="bz-home-heading">官网视觉需要克制，信息必须可验证。</h2>
        <div class="bz-proof-strip" aria-label="白泽明理信任线索">
          <div class="bz-proof-strip__item">
            <div class="bz-proof-strip__k">01 / Explain</div>
            <div class="bz-proof-strip__v">边界清楚</div>
            <p class="bz-proof-strip__b">先解释能力、风险和人工审查位置，再谈自动化收益。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bz-proof-strip__item">
            <div class="bz-proof-strip__k">02 / Verify</div>
            <div class="bz-proof-strip__v">过程可验</div>
            <p class="bz-proof-strip__b">用 SOP、测试、评审和样例证明工作流真实可用。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bz-proof-strip__item">
            <div class="bz-proof-strip__k">03 / Adopt</div>
            <div class="bz-proof-strip__v">组织复用</div>
            <p class="bz-proof-strip__b">把个人经验沉淀成团队可以持续继承的 Skills 与规范。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="bz-rail-section bz-rail-section--alt">
    <div class="bz-shell">
      <div class="bz-home-contact">
        <div>
          <h2 class="bz-home-contact__title">从一次 AI 落地诊断开始。</h2>
          <p class="bz-home-contact__body">如果团队已经在使用 Codex、Claude Code、Cursor 或内部知识库，但缺少统一方法，白泽明理可以先帮你拆出最小可验证路径。</p>
        </div>
        <a class="bz-button bz-button--primary bz-button--lg" href="mailto:fxai.labs@gmail.com">联系白泽明理</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
